@* 포트폴리오 섹션(PC): [대표 영상 16:9 | 우측 340px 영상 목록] — SPEC.PLAYERDASHBOARD.md §4
   대표 영상·목록은 데이터가 있을 때만 렌더. 영상이 없으면 현재 상태 + 등록 가이드 안내 *@
@using PlayGround.Client.Styles
@using PlayGround.Contracts.Player

<div class="flex flex-col gap-[18px]">
    <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
        <h1 class="@Css.Dashboard.SectionTitle">포트폴리오</h1>
        <button type="button" class="@Css.Dashboard.PrimaryButton">＋ 영상 추가</button>
    </div>

    @if (Videos.Count > 0)
    {
        <div class="@(Primary is null ? "flex flex-col gap-3" : "grid grid-cols-[1fr_340px] gap-[18px] items-start")">
            @if (Primary is not null)
            {
                <div class="@($"{Css.Dashboard.Card} overflow-hidden")">
                    <a href="@Primary.VideoUrl" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="block w-full aspect-video relative bg-navy-deep">
                        @if (Primary.ThumbnailUrl is not null)
                        {
                            <img src="@Primary.ThumbnailUrl" alt="대표 영상 썸네일" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover" />
                        }
                        <span class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center pointer-events-none">
                            <span class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-black/[.65] flex items-center justify-center">
                                <svg width="21" height="21" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#fff"><path d="M8 5.5l11 6.5-11 6.5z"></path></svg>
                            </span>
                        </span>
                        <span class="absolute top-3 left-3 text-[11px] font-bold text-white bg-orange rounded-full px-3 py-1 pointer-events-none">대표 영상</span>
                    </a>
                    <div class="px-[22px] py-[18px] flex flex-col gap-[9px]">
                        <div class="flex gap-[7px] items-center">
                            <BrandIcon Type="BrandIcon.BrandIconType.YouTube" Size="15" />
                            <span class="text-[15px] font-extrabold text-navy-deep break-keep">@Primary.Title</span>
                        </div>
                        @if (Primary.Tags.Count > 0)
                        {
                            <div class="flex gap-[7px] flex-wrap">
                                @foreach (string tag in Primary.Tags)
                                {
                                    <span class="text-[11.5px] font-bold text-navy bg-surface-icon rounded-full px-[11px] py-[3px] whitespace-nowrap">@tag</span>
                                }
                            </div>
                        }
                        <span class="text-[12.5px] text-text-muted break-keep">공개 프로필과 선수 카드의 첫 화면에 노출됩니다</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            }

            <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
                <h3 class="m-0 text-[15px] font-extrabold text-navy-deep">영상 목록 <span class="text-xs font-bold text-text-muted">@(Others.Count)개</span></h3>
                @foreach (PlayerPortfolioVideoDto clip in Others)
                {
                    <a href="@clip.VideoUrl" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
                       class="@($"{Css.Dashboard.Card} rounded-[13px] p-3 flex gap-3 items-center hover:border-navy transition-colors")">
                        <div class="w-[110px] aspect-video rounded-lg overflow-hidden relative bg-navy-deep shrink-0">
                            @if (clip.ThumbnailUrl is not null)
                            {
                                <img src="@clip.ThumbnailUrl" alt="썸네일" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover" />
                            }
                            @if (clip.DurationSeconds is not null)
                            {
                                <span class="absolute bottom-1 right-1 text-[9.5px] font-bold text-white bg-black/75 rounded px-[5px] py-px pointer-events-none">@FormatDuration(clip.DurationSeconds.Value)</span>
                            }
                        </div>
                        <span class="flex flex-col gap-[3px] flex-1 min-w-0">
                            <span class="text-[12.5px] font-bold text-navy-deep leading-[1.4] break-keep">@clip.Title</span>
                            @if (clip.RecordedOn is not null)
                            {
                                <span class="text-[11px] text-text-muted whitespace-nowrap">@FormatDate(clip.RecordedOn.Value)</span>
                            }
                        </span>
                    </a>
                }
            </div>
        </div>
    }
    else
    {
        @* 빈 상태: 현재 상태 + 등록 가이드 (주 액션은 헤더의 ＋ 영상 추가 하나 유지) *@
        <div class="bg-white border-1.5 border-dashed border-border rounded-[16px] px-6 py-14 flex flex-col items-center gap-2.5 text-center">
            <svg width="30" height="30" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-text-faint"><rect x="3" y="5" width="18" height="14.5" rx="3"></rect><path d="M10 9.5l5 3-5 3z"></path></svg>
            <span class="text-[15px] font-extrabold text-navy-deep">아직 등록된 영상이 없어요</span>
            <span class="text-[13px] text-text-body leading-[1.7] break-keep">＋ 영상 추가로 유튜브 링크를 등록해 보세요.<br />대표 영상은 공개 프로필과 선수 카드의 첫 화면에 노출돼요.</span>
        </div>
    }
</div>

@code {
    [Parameter, EditorRequired]
    public List<PlayerPortfolioVideoDto> Videos { get; set; } = new();

    internal PlayerPortfolioVideoDto? Primary => Videos.FirstOrDefault(v => v.IsPrimary);

    internal List<PlayerPortfolioVideoDto> Others => Videos.Where(v => !v.IsPrimary).ToList();

    // 92초 → "1:32"
    internal static string FormatDuration(int seconds)
    {
        return $"{seconds / 60}:{seconds % 60:00}";
    }

    // 7월 5일 → "7/5"
    internal static string FormatDate(DateOnly date)
    {
        return $"{date.Month}/{date.Day}";
    }
}
